task.summary: Improvements to Collection indexing. Get now gets intrinsic properties (at least if they are not nested, not tested with nesting) Improvements to Postgres Resource system. More comments about the resources being paralleled with the Abstract Classes.
Improved Postgres Resources and Abstract System, made good progress towards coherence.

Postgres Table Resource has the get_columns_metadata function. Decision has been made to have get_metadata and get_[subitem]_metadata functions. Provides a lot of data obtained through queries in a POJO.
Postgres Table Resource: get_metadata() Improved system of getting metadata, more structured functions.
Commented out most log instructions Having problems with too many Tables (resources and/or abstract) being created in Postgres system, still working on it.

I meant console logs rather than comments last time. Fixed creation of Abstract Columns so that tables have the correct number of them, though only tested for some initialization scenarios. Commented out much console logging.

Made Database Resource .ensure function. Comments there. It makes* Abstract SQL commands to change one Abstract DB into another (Postgres).
* When complete

More work on the Postgres DB system Made comparison-based-change-generator.js which will generate (Postgres) abstract syntax to carry out changes based on comparisons between abstract (models of) databases.
Latest work on the Postgres system

Work on Abstract Postgres comparisons of objects.
More work on the database system, fix to essentials clone function and call_multi
